findings.suggested_fix:
In `infra/terraform/variables.tf`, add:
```hcl
variable "opcert_admin_principal_arns" {
  type = list(string)
  validation {
    condition     = length(var.opcert_admin_principal_arns) > 0 && !contains(var.opcert_admin_principal_arns, "*")
    error_message = "opcert_admin_principal_arns must be non-empty and must not contain wildcard '*'."
  }
}
```
And add AC1 sub-claim (h) asserting the trust policy Principal is never `"*"`.
